{
  "texts": [
    "While the feature is not yet developed, Chat GPT may have the ability to adjust its teaching style and track students' progress based on the context of a conversation.",
    "Furthermore, medical students can improve their knowledge in real-time by utilizing Chat GPT in conjunction with a virtual histology slide application.",
    "Chat GPT can already create self-assessment tests with explanations for the answers [17].",
    "\"Chat GPT -Reshaping Medical Education and Clinical Management\" by Khan et al.",
    "discusses the potential of Chat GPT in reshaping medical education and clinical management."
  ]
}